Name: athena-discuss
Summary: A conferencing and mail archiving system
Copyright: MIT
Group: Applications/Communications

Requires: athena-krb5 athena-zephyr athena-libet

%pre
mkdir -p /var/spool/discuss
touch /var/spool/discuss/.k{5,}login
grep -s -q ^discuss /etc/passwd \
	|| useradd	-d /var/spool/discuss \
			-g 101 \
			-u 32000 \
			-s /dev/null \
			-M \
			discuss

%triggerin -- setup
grep -s -q ^discuss /etc/services \
	|| echo "discuss	2100/tcp	# Networked conferencing." \
		>> /etc/services

%description
Discuss is a user-interface front end to a networked conferencing system.  
